title: Granówko, Choszczno County
data: Granówko [ɡraˈnufkɔ] is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Krzęcin, within Choszczno County, West Pomeranian Voivodeship, in north-western Poland.[1] For the history of the region, see History of Pomerania.
